When the heat is up, take a break and head to Knott's Soak City Water Park in Orange County/Buena Park! With 10 slides and attractions, this park has an array of fun activities for the wet and wild ones in your party! Choose from Banzai Falls that is complete with six speed lane slides from a height of 41 feet, Laguna Storm Water Tower (terrifying 43 foot drop tube slides), Malibu Run inner-tube slides or Old Man Falls at a staggering 63 feet high, Pacific Spin for a multi-person raft ride.For your little ones, don't give the Gremmie Lagoon a miss. This is a large play pool area designed to keep the kids engaged and having fun with an interactive octopus, and other ocean themed landmarks. There is also a lazy river called Sunset River which stretches out of 1780 feet. Looking for a bit of surf action? Head on over to Tidal Wave Bay.Don't forget that Knott's Soak City Water Park also offers shopping and dining options!Current Knott’s Soak City Buena Park Printable Coupons and Savings for 2024

